title: Behind the Smoke Curtain
description:
Behind the Smoke Curtain - 2013 - ISO Image File

What happened at the Pentagon on 9/11, and what didn't, and why it matters.

Barbara Honegger, former Reagan White House policy analyst, presents evidence and high-ranking official eyewitness accounts that prove the Pentagon was bombed with pre-planted explosives and that Flight 77 did not hit the Pentagon on 9/11.

Filmed in Seattle, January 12, 2013 at Town Hall Theater.
